dth":787,"height":151,"file_path":"/uGUeQm8Ww3CYJY4nxcb5w5b2jCV.png","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":0.166},{"width":3049,"height":969,"file_path":"/v4CPglRXXgXtzrzNGcx3BVrCXae.png","iso_639_1":"zh","vote_average":0}],"posters":[{"width":827,"height":1180,"file_path":"/aeklmDwma2WjAOTKlD0r4mwRXVI.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","vote_average":3.334},{"width":967,"height":1450,"file_path":"/tPR5ecnXLypzOdEV5TLxQ8CkczF.jpg","iso_639_1":"es","vote_average":3.334},{"width":904,"height":1356,"file_path":"/9ZfNS44SZQd13EVUSu0VwEo7y18.jpg","iso_639_1":"ko","vote_average":3.334},{"width":1000,"height":1500,"file_path":"/gqGZehMFRo2fnrSxWUitCH8cLfi.jpg","iso_639_1":"pt","vote_average":3.334},{"width":904,"height":1356,"file_path":"/5VXiPw9lrdGcZ2SWbmMFcTfHbD5.jpg","iso_639_1":"ko","vote_average":3.334},{"width":2000,"height":3000,"file_path":"/wiVne6bRE8o3sbBK9K4JdxilZZb.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","vote_average":3.334},{"width":2000,"height":3000,"file_path":"/g9f1BvyPXA9M7HizQDryENZgYV5.jpg","iso_639_1":"ko","vote_average":3.334},{"width":1365,"height":2048,"file_path":"/12FqLZjI9ooglSh2X29u6yoS3mf.jpg","iso_639_1":"ko","vote_average":1.75},{"width":1000,"height":1500,"file_path":"/vyG8qpimh3XSlxc6OmPq8LJRJl.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":1.75},{"width":832,"height":1140,"file_path":"/1Q1P9ghOYXvjPCGkj8idHFRC9LE.jpg","iso_639_1":"es","vote_average":0.166},{"width":700,"height":1000,"file_path":"/k3bo5KezwUNMR0yxdYKZk9kMei7.jpg","iso_639_1":"pt","vote_average":0.166},{"width":900,"height":1282,"file_path":"/ninULGkq7DyvjNKiNskvOwKzMkh.jpg","iso_639_1":"ko","vote_average":0.166},{"width":898,"height":1280,"file_path":"/5Wp45Quc4fo0ChruhFNrXVmOllH.jpg","iso_639_1":"ko","vote_average":0.166},{"width":666,"height":1000,"file_path":"/ywYmahjyBAEYye26vLAMlcNMcKX.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":0},{"width":2000,"height":3000,"file_path":"/vvFaitgXDrQZSPdENiMFwjTNvgu.jpg","iso_639_1":"de","vote_average":0}],"backdrops":[{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/oqaKsofz49zjNhi48sxQIq8U73X.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/dx3c5kdZUNDZujNv2XvHrqR3kMN.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.222},{"width":1446,"height":813,"file_path":"/5fSiKlAibnZetnWjIQRnFVeknKq.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/2hBeVVxdA6LBKohatNXmAmfzc0k.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/kyhzxMIv6LEUeVPkOCZnpqQmW7T.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/6CeuXfrqe9TCBBaFTwvb6tnjIc9.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-21T16:03:25.353+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Tae Guk Gi: The Brotherhood of War","runtime":148,"tagline":"One country, one family… divided by war.","homepage":"","overview":"When two brothers are forced to fight in the Korean War, the elder decides to take the riskiest missions if it will help shield the younger from battle."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Brotherhood","runtime":140,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Die Brüder Jin-Tae und Jin-Seok werden bei Ausbruch des Koreakrieges 1950 von der südkoreanischen Regierung eingezogen und müssen Familie und Habseligkeiten zurücklassen. Jin-Tae, der selbst die Schule abgebrochen hat und ein eher rauher Bursche ist, versucht seinen zartbesaiteten Bruder vor den Gefahren des Krieges zu schützen, indem er sich stets vor ihn stellt. Hierzu nimmt Jin-Tae oftmals gefährliche Missionen an und zeigt dabei, dass er durchaus eine gewisse Begabung für den Krieg hat. Seine Beliebtheit unter den anderen Soldaten nimmt stetig zu, jedoch verändert sich seine Person zunehmend. Jin-Seok stellt sich immer mehr die Frage, ob sein Bruder wirklich für ihn und seine Familie kämpft oder aus eigennützigem Medaillenehrgeiz."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Kardeşler Savaşı","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Kore Savaşı’ndan yıllar sonra, savaş alanda yapılan bir kazı Jin Tae Lee'yi geçmişe götürür. Kazıdan çıkan bazı eşyalarla savaş sırasında kaybolan ağabeyinden bir ize ulaşabileceğini uman Jin Tae sayesinde 1950-53 yıllarında iki ülke arasında patlak veren savaşa tanık oluruz.  Savaş çıkmadan önce üniversite öğrencisi olan Jin Tae Lee, ağabeyi ile ayakkabı tamirciliği yapmaktadır. Annesi ve ağabeyinin nişanlısı ile kurdukları mutlu ve sıradan bir yaşamları vardır. Ağabeyi bir yandan annesine ve kardeşine bakarken, diğer yandan da evlilik hazırlıkları yapmaktadır.  Her şey normal giderken Kuzey Kore ve Güney Kore arasında savaş çanları çalar. Aile göç etmek durumunda kalır fakat iki kardeş yolculukları esnasında askere alınırlar. Ağabey Jin Seok'un hayattaki tek bir amacı artık savaştan sağ salim ve zaferle çıkarak ailesinin yanına dönmektir..."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Frères de sang","runtime":140,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Séoul, Corée du Sud, au début des années 50.Jin-tae est un cireur de chaussures qui consacre ses modestes ressources à l'éducation de son frère cadet, Jin-suk, et espère envoyer prochainement celui-ci à l'Université. Leur mère, veuve et handicapée, tient une échoppe avec l'aide de la fiancée de Jin-tae, Young-shin, qu'elle a recueillie quelques années plus tôt. Tous les espoirs de cette famille s'effondrent brutalement le 25 juin 1950, lorsque la guerre éclate. Jin-suk est recruté de force et envoyé sur le front. Jin-tae tente vainement d'intercéder, et subit le même sort. Les deux frères rejoignent cette armée du Sud, mal équipée, mal nourrie, mal organisée, harcelée jour et nuit par un ennemi supérieur en nombre et en force..."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"38-я параллель","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"На фоне трагических событий корейской войны 1950-53 годов - самой кровопролитной после окончания Второй мировой, показана судьба одной семьи. Мирное благополучие, счастливые ожидания, мечты и надежды рушатся в единый миг, когда страну охватывает хаос и ужас войны. Под грохот танков, свист пуль и разрывы бомб главный герой фильма Джин-тае пытается спасти своих близких, отправив их на кажущийся спокойным юг Корейского полуострова. Семья, присоединившаяся к колоннам беженцев, заполнивших дороги страны, проходит сквозь лишения и испытания. Но главное несчастье ждало Джин-тае впереди. Его младшего брата силой забрали в солдаты. Джин-тае отчаянно пытался помешать рекрутерам, но сам оказался в поезде новобранцев. Неопытных, необученных, плохо вооруженных парней немедленно забрасывают на передовую. Им приказано держать оборону у реки Накдонг и не сдавать позиций. Для верховного командования они - пушечное мясо. Под шквальным огнем у молодых солдат почти нет шансов выжить..."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"A Irmandade da Guerra","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Jin-tae, um sapateiro, trabalha incansavelmente para poder pagar a faculdade de seu irmão mais novo Jin-seok, entretanto, seus desejos e sonhos são colocados de lado quando os dois são forçados a entrar no exército contra suas vontades. No momento crucial da batalha, o destino intervém, forçando seus laços de fé, amor e confiança a serem testados diversas vezes."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Lazos de guerra","runtime":140,"tagline":"Un Film de Kang Je-gyu","homepage":"","overview":"Jin-tae es un zapatero que lleva años trabajando sin descanso para que su hermano menor, Jin-seok, pueda ir a la universidad. Pero todos sus sueños y esperanzas se desvanecen cuando los dos son obligados a incorporarse al ejército en contra de su voluntad. Separado de su casa y de su familia, Jin-tae promete proteger a Jin-sok. Pero la guerra pondrá a prueba sus lazos de fe, amor y confianza."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Harcosok szövetsége","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Archeológusok csoportja egy csontvázat talál, amelyet Lee Jin-seok maradványaiként azonosítanak. Ám Lin Jin-seok nem halt meg, békében élte meg az öregkort. A testvére, Jin-tae viszont eltűnt a koreai háborúban. Megelevenedik a múlt, 1950-ben járunk. A háború kirobbanásakor mindkettőjüket besorozzák a hadseregbe, és a frontvonalra viszik őket. Jin-tae alkut köt a feletteseivel: ha elég hőstettet hajt végre, akkor korábban hazaengedik az öccsét. Minden küldetést elvállal, miközben féltő gondoskodásával szinte megfojtja testvérét. Ám Jin-tae az ellenség fogságába esik."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Brotherhood of War - TaeGukGi","runtime":148,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"I BROTHERHOOD OF WAR får vi under 1950-talet följa två bröder från Söul, som kort efter Koreakrigets utbrott kallas in i armén mot sin vilja. För att rädda sin yngre bror undan kriget kämpar den äldre brodern hårt för att vinna en tapperhetsmedalj. Men allt eftersom kriget och striderna rasar runtomkring dem förlorar han sakta men säkert sitt omdöme bland krigets illgärningar."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"The Brotherhood of War","runtime":140,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"In 1950 breekt er oorlog uit tussen het communistische Noord-Korea en het kapitalistische Zuid-Korea. Terwijl ze met hun familie op de vlucht zijn worden twee broers meegenomen naar het front, om daar te vechten voor de vrijheid van hun volk."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"太极旗飘扬","runtime":148,"tagline":"一个国家，一个家庭…被战争分割。","homepage":"","overview":"　　李镇泰是生活在汉城的一个修鞋匠，一家人的生计就从修补鞋子的费用维持。虽然物质并不富裕，这却是一个十分温馨完整的家庭。妻子李英顺和母亲开一间面馆，平日还要照顾下面的弟妹，弟弟李镇锡是家中所有的希望，如今正在高中读书，考上大学是他的梦想，更是哥哥镇泰的寄托所在。然而随着1950年朝鲜战争突然爆发，平静的生活很快被打乱。战火蔓延汉城，镇泰决定带着家人到大邱去生活，躲避战乱。但在中途，他们却被强行征入军队，押上了开往洛东江前线的列车。从此一家人四分五裂。而在战场上的镇泰只剩下一个愿望：不顾一切用生命保护弟弟，当听说只要获得国家勋章就可以让弟弟免役时，他便疯子般冲在战斗最前沿。然而残酷的战场加上弄人的命运，他们的生命轨迹发生了无可避免的改变。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Brotherhood of war","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Brotherhood Of War - TaeGukGi – fortæller historien om to brødre fra Seoul, som, da Korea-krigen begynder i 1950, bliver indkaldt til hæren mod deres vilje. Den ældste bror kæmper hårdt for at gøre sig fortjent til en tapperhedsmedalje, så han kan sikre sin lillebrors hjemsendelse. Men han ændrer fuldstændigt personlighed i takt med, at krigshelvedet intensiveres."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"Sotto due bandiere","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Due fratelli, un unico destino. Siamo negli anni '50, in Oriente sta per esplodere una delle prime micce della Guerra Fredda: la guerra di Corea. Jin-tae e Jin-seok vengono coinvolti nel conflitto contro gli invasori comunisti del Nord, ma reagiscono in maniera diametralmente opposta. Il fratello maggiore si rende protagonista di imprese eroiche diventando in breve una macchina da guerra; il più piccolo ripudia l'atrocità della violenza. I due vivranno così un conflitto nel conflitto."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":148,"tagline":"우린 반드시 살아서 돌아가야 해","homepage":"","overview":"1950년 6월. 서울 종로에서 가족의 생계를 책임지기 위해 열심히 살아가는 진태는 힘든 생활 속에도 약혼녀 영신과의 결혼과, 세상에서 가장 소중하게 생각하는 동생 진석의 대학진학을 위해 언제나 활기차고 밝은 생활을 해 나간다. 6월의 어느 날, 한반도에 전쟁이 일어났다는 호외가 배포되면서 평화롭기만 하던 서울은 순식간에 싸이렌 소리와 폭발음, 그리고 사람들의 비명 소리로 가득해진다. 이에 남쪽으로 피난을 결정한 진태는 영신과 가족들을 데리고 수많은 피난행렬에 동참하지만, 피난열차를 타기 위해 도착한 대구역사에서 거대한 운명의 소용돌이에 말려들고 만다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"אחוות המלחמה","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"כאשר קבוצת ארכיאולוגים קוראינית מוצאים גופה ומזהים אותה, הם קוראים ל לי ג'ין-סוק אשר עכשיו הוא אדם מבוגר, ומספרים לו שמצאו את גופת אחיו אשר מת במלחמת קוריאה. אנחנו נוסעים אחורה בזמן לשנת 1950 כאשר מלחמת קוריאה בתחילתה האחים לי-ג'ין סוק וג'ין-טי, אשר היו צעירים מוצאים עצמם בעולם שכולו דם אשר ממש שונה מהעולם שאנו מכירים. בהמשך המלחמה ג'ין-טי משתגע."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Pouta války","runtime":140,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Aby mohl svého mladšího bratra poslat na studia, je Jin-Tae ochotný si vydělávat na ulici jako čistič bot. Společně s ovdovělou matkou se upnou k akademické budoucnosti Jin-Seoka jako ke svému cíli. V Koreji však vypukne válka a benjamínek rodiny musí rukovat. Zodpovědnost a strach o bratra přivedou i Jin-Taea do války. V okamžiku, kdy začne válečná vřava ohrožovat životy obou, rozhodne se Jin-Tae přihlásit na sebevražednou misi, aby vysloužil bratrovi odchod do civilu. Ten Jin-Taeův plán zprvu nechápe a odsuzuje jej jako zbytečně vlasteneckou honbu za slávou. Tae Guk Gi je korejský název pro státní vlajku Jižní Koreje s mandalou a čtyřmi trigramy."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"A Irmandade da Guerra","runtime":0,"tagline":"Um país, uma família… dividida pela guerra.","homepage":"","overview":"Jin-tae, um sapateiro, trabalha incansavelmente para poder pagar a faculdade de seu irmão mais novo Jin-seok, entretanto, seus desejos e sonhos são colocados de lado quando os dois são forçados a entrar no exército contra suas vontades. No momento crucial da batalha, o destino intervém, forçando seus laços de fé, amor e confiança a serem testados diversas vezes."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Braterstwo broni","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Opowieść powracająca do krwawych wydarzeń, które rozgrywały się w Korei w latach 1950-1953 i kosztowały życie ponad miliona ofiar. Na tle wojny domowej toczy się dramatyczna historia dwóch braci, Jin-tae i Jin-seoka, którzy pod przymusem zostają wcieleni do armii i wysłani na front. Straszy z nich dokonuje wielu bohaterskich czynów, byle tylko uchronić młodszego, chorego na serce Jin-seoka, przed śmiercią. W ogniu walki i wobec wszechobecnego okrucieństwa ich wzajemna miłość i zaufanie zostają poddane najcięższej próbie."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Войната на братята","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"През 1950, в Южна Корея, чистачът на обувки Джин-тае Ли и 18-годишният му брат студент, Джин-сок Ли, оформят бедно, но щастливо семейство заедно с майка им, годеницата на Джин-тае и нейните сестри. Когато Северна Корея напада Южна Корея, семейството е принудено да бяга, но по пътя Джин-сок е принуден да се присъедини към армията, а брат му се записва, за да го защитава. На фона на кървавата война отношенията им постепенно се влошават и достигат трагичен край."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Розмах національного прапора","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"У фільмі розповідається про події Корейської війни 1950–1953 років. Основна увага приділяється трагедії корейської родини: два брати в силу обставин опинилися по різні боки барикад. Творцям фільму вдалося надзвичайно гостро показати жахливість братовбивчих воєн, несправедливість і жорстокість та, одночасно, і нагадати, що самопожертва і любов до ближнього притаманні людині навіть у найжорстокіший час."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"La hermandad de la guerra","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Un soldado se ve atrapado en la violencia de la batalla mientras intenta proteger a su hermano menor en la guerra de Corea."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Tae Guk Gi - Frăția războiului","runtime":140,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"De la regizorul lui Shiri vine și povestea celor doi frați. Jin-tae, pantofar de meserie, a muncit neîncetat din nevoia de bani pentru ca mai tânărul Jin-seok să meargă la facultate.\r Toate speranțele și visele lor sunt spulberate când amândoi sunt obligați să se înroleze în armată împotriva voinței lor. Departe de familie și prieteni, Jin-tae jură să-l protejeze cu orice preț pe Jin-seok în pofida pericolelor. În vâltoarea luptei intervine soarta, forțându-le limitele credinței, dragostei și încrederii în această dramă de război plină de suspans și acțiune."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"太極旗飄揚：生死有情","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"韓戰於 1950 年爆發，中國與北韓聯手對付麥克阿瑟率領的聯合國軍隊展開了歷時三年的戰爭。從未受過正式軍事訓練的振太 (張東健飾) 和振錫 (元斌飾) 被強召入伍。振太為求弟弟可以豁免軍役，不惜參加自殺式襲擊行動，冒死贏取「榮譽勳章」，希望以此作為換取弟弟回家的條件。但單純善良的振錫卻以為哥哥藉拯救他離開戰場為藉口，來掩飾自己虛榮貪功的野心。隨著戰況癒加激烈，以及一次比一次危險的自殺式襲擊行動，兩兄弟之間的誤會和衝突不斷加劇。直至振鍚看到一封哥哥寫給母親的家書，才真正明瞭哥哥的用心，他隨即作出了一個出乎意外的決定…"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"太極旗－生死兄弟","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"1950年6月24日。為了全家人的生計，振泰（張東健飾）每天在漢城鍾路為人擦皮鞋，日子雖然過得辛苦，但只要一想到因自己的努力而終於步入大學校園的弟弟振錫（元斌飾），還有即將與戀人英信〈李銀珠飾〉結婚而充滿希望和幸福時，他就感到無比欣慰。  可是正當振泰沉浸在自己的幸福世界時，突如其來的噩耗卻改變了一切。有一天，從學校歸來的振錫，漲紅著臉告訴振泰即將爆發戰爭的消息。同一時間，收音機的廣播裏、外面的街道上，到處彌漫著戰爭的氣氛。滿載大兵的軍用卡車和軍事演練一次又一次的經過面前，街上人群神色匆忙，一下子昔日繁華的鍾路陷入了一片混亂之中。而遠處不斷傳來的轟炸聲、喊救命的聲音，還有越來越多的運屍車，都讓振泰強烈意識到戰爭的來臨。  振泰於是慌慌張張打包行囊帶著一家人和英信的弟妹們一起加入避難行列，大家唯恐走散所以手拉著手緊緊相隨，最後終於在灰土交加中到大邱。可就此時，振泰和振錫兄弟倆稀裏糊塗地被推上了軍用列車，此時此刻他們才知道自己已被強行徵兵而即將奔赴前線。  被強行徵兵的振泰不得不拋下曾應允今年秋天就娶進家門的英信和身體欠恙的母親，和弟弟振錫一起從軍去了。振泰和振錫被拉到了每天吞噬數千數萬人生命的戰場，而參戰的振泰的唯一心願，就是寧死也要讓弟弟振錫活著回家。於是，振泰懷著只要自己在戰場上立功獲勳章即可讓弟弟活著回家的希望，不顧一切地投身到這場無法預知的殘酷戰爭中…而單純善良的振錫在這場血雨腥風的戰爭中也不失其純淨的心靈，他一邊經歷著殘酷的戰爭，一邊成長……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"The Brotherhood of War","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Όταν δύο αδέλφια αναγκάζονται να πολεμήσουν στον πόλεμο της Κορέας, ο μεγαλύτερος αποφασίζει να αναλάβει τις πιο ριψοκίνδυνες αποστολές για να προστατέψει τον νεότερο στη μάχη."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"เท กึก กี เลือดเนื้อเพื่อฝัน วันสิ้นสงคราม","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"38 პარალელი","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"თხეგიკი - კორეის ნაციონალური დროშის სახელია. ფილმის ერთ-ერთი გმირის დავალებაა ამ დროშის პეკტუსანის მთაზე აღმართვა, კორეის ომის დროს, კომუნიზმზე გამარჯვების ნიშნად. ეს ფილმი არის ორ ძმაზე, რომლებიც ტრაგიკულმა გარემოებამ ერთმანეთს გაჰყარა."},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"ブラザーフッド","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Frères de sang","runtime":140,"tagline":"Un pays, une famille… séparés par la guerre.","homepage":"","overview":"Séoul, Corée du Sud, au début des années 50.Jin-tae est un cireur de chaussures qui consacre ses modestes ressources à l'éducation de son frère cadet, Jin-suk, et espère envoyer prochainement celui-ci à l'Université. Leur mère, veuve et handicapée, tient une échoppe avec l'aide de la fiancée de Jin-tae, Young-shin, qu'elle a recueillie quelques années plus tôt. Tous les espoirs de cette famille s'effondrent brutalement le 25 juin 1950, lorsque la guerre éclate. Jin-suk est recruté de force et envoyé sur le front. Jin-tae tente vainement d'intercéder, et subit le même sort. Les deux frères rejoignent cette armée du Sud, mal équipée, mal nourrie, mal organisée, harcelée jour et nuit par un ennemi supérieur en nombre et en force..."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":407887,"adult":false,"title":"Operation Chromite","video":false,"overview":"A squad of soldiers fight in the Korean War's crucial Battle of Incheon.","genre_ids":[36,18,10752,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.6618,"vote_count":221,"poster_path":"/c9Md7hQTNjFUZF0LgpWpVCS1GcI.jpg","release_date":"2016-07-27","vote_average":5.808,"backdrop_path":"/61fTz1JnqsWm5a8wV3bUnw6IoQk.jpg","original_title":"인천상륙작전","original_language":"ko"},{"id":94047,"adult":false,"title":"My Way","video":false,"overview":"During the invasion of Normandy the photograph of a slim Korean man in German uniform was found. It transpired that the man had served as a soldier in the Japanese, Russian and German armies. His incredible story inspired director Kang Je-Gyu to create this epic war drama.","genre_ids":[18,28,36,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.9984,"vote_count":433,"poster_path":"/3moPqIC1EBFilLI3YJNa5Nfel3e.jpg","release_date":"2011-12-21","vote_average":7.886,"backdrop_path":"/4QHF7kAYjIpZ5U8A0amvhRkHlZ1.jpg","original_title":"마이웨이","original_language":"ko"},{"id":24293,"adult":false,"title":"Goemon","video":false,"overview":"Follow the infamous ninja bandit named Ishikawa Goemon (Yosuke Eguchi) in an epic story. One night while looting treasure from Nanban (Southern Barbarians), Goemon finds a mysterious box hidden inside a secret grave. A forgotten relic from the past containing untold powers.","genre_ids":[28,18,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8806,"vote_count":128,"poster_path":"/kHo5yDjgpH5brCT2wCgjW2HdSLq.jpg","release_date":"2009-03-17","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/2oEbG4dwwzjcaXYvMJkMV3idBOb.jpg","original_title":"Goemon","original_language":"ja"},{"id":41091,"adult":false,"title":"...ing","video":false,"overview":"Follows the life of a young woman who has become reserved and indifferent to the world as a result of her chronic illness deformed hand and quietly portrays the unconventional, yet endearing relationship between mother and daughter as well as the development of Min-ah as she is befriended by the high spirited and carefree photographer Young-jae who moves into their apartment complex.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5389,"vote_count":58,"poster_path":"/bUy74ts2Ru4mOjXUGzWP1Gs3LG.jpg","release_date":"2003-11-28","vote_average":6.698,"backdrop_path":"/u6WDU3Z1d6y0ybisMYiDFwt0YHq.jpg","original_title":"...ing","original_language":"ko"},{"id":329253,"adult":false,"title":"Salut d'Amour","video":false,"overview":"Sung-chil works at the Jang-soo Store which is owned by Jang-soo. Sung-chil is stubborn and has a bad temper, but he changes after meeting Geum-nim. Geun-nim runs a flower shop and her daughter Min-jung does not like her meeting Sung-chil.","genre_ids":[35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7277,"vote_count":23,"poster_path":"/zOaSxeHzzDym3Qsxwi3fF6myfT5.jpg","release_date":"2015-04-09","vote_average":7.891,"backdrop_path":"/iUgvTjYY8rjQ5omQmVmHrt7iWxj.jpg","original_title":"장수상회","original_language":"ko"},{"id":120243,"adult":false,"title":"No. 3","video":false,"overview":"Tae-joo manages to rise in rank in a gang for saving the boss's life. However, prosecutor Dong-pal appears in front of him as his sworn enemy. Meanwhile, Jo-pil wants to get rid of Tae-joo's gang, training for revenge. The three men's goals intertwine.","genre_ids":[18,28,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2891,"vote_count":27,"poster_path":"/z0GIab04HMzRYZJkzts0X0D5G4M.jpg","release_date":"1997-08-02","vote_average":6.196,"backdrop_path":"/uXaVPgIMNR4uhVOcRyVkoyZQOTK.jpg","original_title":"넘버 3","original_language":"ko"},{"id":23908,"adult":false,"title":"A Midnight Clear","video":false,"overview":"In 1944 France, an American Intelligence Squad locates a German Platoon wishing to surrender rather than die in Germany's final war offensive. The two groups of men, isolated from the war at present, put aside their differences and spend Christmas together before the surrender plan turns bad and both sides are forced to fight the other.","genre_ids":[18,10752,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8287,"vote_count":121,"poster_path":"/cOLBAnK2PvHxwjdEHQl4n3pZI14.jpg","release_date":"1992-04-24","vote_average":6.521,"backdrop_path":"/qDDaOIwlahViQMFMOnPeBYcUp3X.jpg","original_title":"A Midnight Clear","original_language":"en"},{"id":19588,"adult":false,"title":"My Boss, My Hero","video":false,"overview":"When a young gang leader seems to be just a bit too stupid to effectively carry out his daily tasks, his superiors order him to go back to school for his high school diploma. Posing as a 19-year-old, he soon learns that the school is even more corrupt and vicious. Wrath is unleashed.","genre_ids":[28,35,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0661,"vote_count":29,"poster_path":"/iOyWhkeDJ7GY2VcA93KF0oLzLV6.jpg","release_date":"2001-12-14","vote_average":5.966,"backdrop_path":"/ovLJAwkA28f8lwLL5PqfmnkyLk1.jpg","original_title":"두사부일체","original_language":"ko"},{"id":38019,"adult":false,"title":"Sunflower","video":false,"overview":"Sunflower is the story of the Zhang family in Beijing father, mother and son across three decades, centering on the tensions and misunderstandings between father and son. Nine-year-old Xiangyang is having the time of his life, free of adult supervision until the day he meets the father he can hardly remember. Having spent years away, he returns with strong ideas about his son learning to draw. But Xiangyang chafes under his father's constant rules and soon stages his own revolution against the lessons enforced.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6001,"vote_count":15,"poster_path":"/d7NsjHTppTK8KfFBJRk6J4Su6ct.jpg","release_date":"2005-09-10","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/7cJ49ORSne1wrQ383m6eEKAECgN.jpg","original_title":"向日葵","original_language":"zh"},{"id":519291,"adult":false,"title":"Pluto's Greatest Hits","video":false,"overview":"- The Moose Hunt [1931]  - Pluto, Junior  - Bone Trouble  - The Legend of Coyote Rock  - Donald and Pluto  - The Army Mascot  - Pluto's Blue Note","genre_ids":[35,16],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0261,"vote_count":15,"poster_path":"/5vPCkWqXarws0DsfomktuBrNSLE.jpg","release_date":"2000-02-06","vote_average":7.7,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Pluto's Greatest Hits","original_language":"en"},{"id":499909,"adult":false,"title":"Why did I write the Bible","video":false,"overview":"Francis, a man in his sixties, is found in a diving suit, swimming in a river in the city center. Even his children, accustomed to their father's escapades, are surprised: since Francis knows he is condemned, it seems really unmanageable. Samuel and his sister must therefore find a way to accompany him at any cost.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0637,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/upfdzlslEnZpllsix16w8ClMgPR.jpg","release_date":"2017-11-28","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Pourquoi j'ai écrit la Bible","original_language":"fr"},{"id":72614,"adult":false,"title":"One-Two, Soldiers Were Going...","video":false,"overview":"The families of 18 soldiers who heroically died in 1944 are meeting at the place of the squad last battle.","genre_ids":[18,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0765,"vote_count":25,"poster_path":"/eoAYfzr0mZSdEC7HeIsCFQdAUMO.jpg","release_date":"1976-06-06","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/cTgk7W9ry1gxyghXAbDe3Ahzr7g.jpg","original_title":"Аты-баты, шли солдаты...","original_language":"ru"},{"id":61083,"adult":false,"title":"Fast Lane to Vegas","video":false,"overview":"Brian and Zack take off for a bachelor blowout in the City of Sin to celebrate Brian's last days as a man free of married life. Las Vegas offers them choices in every frame of desire and fulfillment, from erotic dancers and strippers to the bold and beautiful women who come looking for a good time. Little does Brian realize that his fiancée and her maid of honor are also looking for a little premarriage tension release, and are finding it in equally dishonorable ways.","genre_ids":[35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7813,"vote_count":13,"poster_path":"/ySmVHZRNqm7ACCbBNdi3N6stHTV.jpg","release_date":"2001-03-20","vote_average":3.8,"backdrop_path":"/5LE4PBbsbl5bvwI0UVbGeI4onf5.jpg","original_title":"Fast Lane to Vegas","original_language":"en"},{"id":44534,"adult":false,"title":"Captain from Castile","video":false,"overview":"Spain, 1518: young caballero Pedro De Vargas offends his sadistic neighbor De Silva, who just happens to be an officer of the Inquisition. Forced to flee, Pedro, friend Juan Garcia, and adoring servant girl Catana join Cortez' first expedition to Mexico. Arriving in the rich new land, Cortez decides to switch from exploration to conquest...with only 500 men. Embroiled in continuous adventures and a romantic interlude, Pedro almost forgets he has a deadly enemy...","genre_ids":[12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.782,"vote_count":30,"poster_path":"/5DojmAjGSnISbZLg7C1Bb6dvXVJ.jpg","release_date":"1947-12-25","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/96OBCIrpNckv0B2H2Kag1vQk3UT.jpg","original_title":"Captain from Castile","original_language":"en"},{"id":349201,"adult":false,"title":"Love Wind Love Song","video":false,"overview":"A Seoul businessman comes to Jeju Island and meets a lonely tour guide.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2984,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/ncgpWXarIUfnxcPAlSAuBvjRo9s.jpg","release_date":"1999-02-13","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/6jgmklE2120xNU6VghX2TKe9Ajg.jpg","original_title":"연풍연가","original_language":"ko"},{"id":505951,"adult":false,"title":"Kannum Kannum Kollaiyadithaal","video":false,"overview":"Two wily online scammers mend their fraudulent ways after meeting the girls of their dreams — until a deceitful discovery throws their world for a loop.","genre_ids":[10749,35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4316,"vote_count":76,"poster_path":"/mwIdGye0iAmaHCBAqzfiHoRb0f2.jpg","release_date":"2020-02-28","vote_average":6.855,"backdrop_path":"/ihc061apXLejGlSm0o9zBS096mW.jpg","original_title":"கண்ணும் கண்ணும் கொள்ளையடித்தால்","original_language":"ta"},{"id":40243,"adult":false,"title":"Heavenly Forest","video":false,"overview":"Amateur photographer Makoto and the homely but endearing Shizuru meet during their university entrance ceremony and become instant friends. Shy by nature, Makoto finds himself opening up around Shizuru, who is secretly in love with him.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0311,"vote_count":93,"poster_path":"/uqcKoM8KlgKeMw0XvKhjp3qwUag.jpg","release_date":"2006-10-28","vote_average":7.5,"backdrop_path":"/v41bl9IXnqsZdaBQG6AYQpOMfM8.jpg","original_title":"ただ、君を愛してる","original_language":"ja"},{"id":339533,"adult":false,"title":"San Andreas Quake","video":false,"overview":"When a discredited L.A. Seismologist warns of an impending 12.7 earthquake, no one takes her seriously. Now on her own, she races desperately to get her family to safety before the earthquake breaks Los Angeles apart from the mainland.","genre_ids":[28,878,10770],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5741,"vote_count":192,"poster_path":"/4dx0K5ZbdhQDfcyBqqHJFH1OW71.jpg","release_date":"2015-05-19","vote_average":4.234,"backdrop_path":"/gSArEgFJb4qUYpjhqMApcKmD7Ye.jpg","original_title":"San Andreas Quake","original_language":"en"},{"id":11169,"adult":false,"title":"Spartan","video":false,"overview":"U.S. government agent Scott is assigned to rescue the daughter of a high-ranking government official. As willing as he is to bend the rules to get things done, though, Scott is shocked to find that others are willing to go even further to protect a political career.","genre_ids":[9648,28,18,53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2041,"vote_count":406,"poster_path":"/rcdhS2g1d38NOoeh0PPAN2bLE7w.jpg","release_date":"2004-03-12","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/1dm0kjWhYDcVPyBk0CZRThxwNyK.jpg","original_title":"Spartan","original_language":"en"},{"id":50618,"adult":false,"title":"Fortress of War","video":false,"overview":"The film covers the heroic defence of the Brest Fortress, which was attacked during the first strike of German invaders on June 22 1941. The story describes the events of the first days of the defence, including the three main resistance zones, headed by the regiment commander, Pyotr Mikhailovich Gavrilov, the commissar Efim Moiseevich Fomin and the head of the 9th frontier outpost, Andrey Mitrofanovich Kizhevatov. Many years later veteran Alexander Akimov again recalls the memories of the time, when he, then a 15 year old Sasha Akimov was deeply in love with the beautiful Anya and suddenly found himself in the middle of the bloody events of war.","genre_ids":[10752,18,36,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8291,"vote_count":180,"poster_path":"/6pocaDiLUONtU3bNY57XGPfBqVr.jpg","release_date":"2010-11-04","vote_average":7.172,"backdrop_path":"/6AXiXs5BOaGpYx1ctChTSNJxjJu.jpg","original_title":"Брестская крепость","original_language":"ru"}],"similar_content":[{"id":249573,"adult":false,"title":"Tokyo File 212","video":false,"overview":"A Communist spy ring in Japan is hard at work trying to sabotage the American war effort during the Korean War, using kidnapping, murder and a disturbed former kamikaze pilot. A U.S. secret agent, posing as a reporter, is dispatched to Tokyo to put a stop to these nefarious activities.","genre_ids":[80,18],"popularity":0.2362,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/drVgjWGZU0RgEpEOJYUEV3KBO0A.jpg","release_date":"1951-01-26","vote_average":4.5,"backdrop_path":"/f8RQg7fH7c7BdZoZ48TnXNtT4La.jpg","original_title":"Tokyo File 212","original_language":"en"},{"id":435346,"adult":false,"title":"Doctor Who: Genesis of the Daleks","video":true,"overview":"The Time Lords dispatch the Doctor to the past of the planet Skaro on his deadliest adventure yet — to prevent the creation of the Daleks.","genre_ids":[878,12,18],"popularity":0.1592,"vote_count":15,"poster_path":"/qNH2FrVwQ58FusIlaX94jb4Ixkw.jpg","release_date":"1975-04-12","vote_average":8.833,"backdrop_path":"/y3BOrhne4xpUP3T1qvN3PWWBIpF.jpg","original_title":"Doctor Who: Genesis of the Daleks","original_language":"en"},{"id":435366,"adult":false,"title":"Fabricated City","video":false,"overview":"In real life, Kwon Yoo is unemployed, but in the virtual game world he is the best leader. Kwon Yoo is then framed for a murder. With the help of hacker Yeo-wool, he tries to uncover the truth behind the murder case.","genre_ids":[28,53,80],"popularity":2.3314,"vote_count":340,"poster_path":"/8tE4MhhuWHize6pNyxAtakUyNZc.jpg","release_date":"2017-02-09","vote_average":7.7,"backdrop_path":"/wvNCnYb2K5lcfRDhtH65OaWHIvp.jpg","original_title":"조작된 도시","original_language":"ko"},{"id":265340,"adult":false,"title":"Good Windy Days","video":false,"overview":"Three friends, Duk-bae, Chun-sik, and Kil-nam, work each at a suburban Chinese restaurant, a barbershop, and a motel. The three friends are clueless about their future. They just share the drinks and love stories. Kil-nam is in love with Jin-ok working at a hair salon and Chun-sik is after Yu who also works at the barbershop. Naive Duk-bae's mind is torn between Chun-sun who works at a factory and an uptown girl Myung-hi.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.302,"vote_count":9,"poster_path":"/rPGUze2BZtKdqh1pesSlS2k5O6S.jpg","release_date":"1980-11-27","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/jZAoSTLQlrWGziu8xzDjedS5ge5.jpg","original_title":"바람불어 좋은 날","original_language":"ko"},{"id":265342,"adult":false,"title":"Declaration of Fools","video":false,"overview":"Beginning with the suicide of a film director, this work represents the Korean New Wave Cinema movement that focused on criticizing the Korean society in the 1980s through satire and humor. The journey taken by the characters, who lead low lives at the margins of the society, award them with a sense of liberation, however brief.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":0.2823,"vote_count":7,"poster_path":"/jXxGVZ9UGSGTCyCZI6lQMhPyi1P.jpg","release_date":"1983-11-04","vote_average":6.429,"backdrop_path":"/3KkrxTBoXhdRNABZYzvgscXDlEu.jpg","original_title":"바보 선언","original_language":"ko"},{"id":265348,"adult":false,"title":"Grensbasis 13","video":false,"overview":"A story about a fictional South African police base on the border between Angola and the former South West Africa. While patrolling, a mail convoy is ambushed and most of the soldiers are shot. The captain is rescued, but one of his constables is taken prisoner. The constable’s sister is also the captain’s girlfriend. GRENSBASIS 13 (Border Post 13) tells the story of the captain’s suspenseful and action-filled rescue attempt in order to bring his sweetheart’s brother home.","genre_ids":[18,28],"popularity":2.2508,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/sXKUnhB3yhxtIL2ICR8N7stlCvH.jpg","release_date":"1979-05-25","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Grensbasis 13","original_language":"af"},{"id":434724,"adult":false,"title":"The King","video":false,"overview":"A young Korean man surpasses his difficult childhood by becoming a powerful prosecutor, but soon learns that real power comes at a price.","genre_ids":[80,28],"popularity":1.3176,"vote_count":86,"poster_path":"/97UeWeCYcK9gkiZLPNJIj0JDRFi.jpg","release_date":"2017-01-18","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/auA1OaJKbim8E7ACnMYmvHz5wNB.jpg","original_title":"더 킹","original_language":"ko"},{"id":433850,"adult":false,"title":"The Martyrs","video":false,"overview":"Out of fourteen ministers taken away by the communist troop, only two come back alive. The mystery behind their survival is at the issue here. Told through one of the survivor's testimony, 